    • Method Detail

      • init

        public void init(android.content.Context context,
        WigzoStore store,
        boolean raiseExceptions)
        Initialize device ID generation, that is start up required services and send requests. Device ID is expected to be available after some time. In some cases, Wigzo can override ID generation strategy to other one, for example when Google Play Services are not available and user chose Advertising ID strategy, it will fall back to OpenUDID
        Parameters:
        context - Context to use
        store - WigzoStore to store configuration in
        raiseExceptions - whether to raise exceptions in case of illegal state or not
